{
  "text": "The fact that intestinal NT secretion and mRNA expression were altered by manipulations known to change intestinal BA concentration and total BA pool size suggested that NT, which is released during fat ingestion, might regulate BA secretion and/or enterohepatic BA cycling. To test this, we infused rats with a dose of NT shown by us [CITATION_1] to mimic the two-to threefold increase in NT blood level seen after fat ingestion.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "42392984"
